videos.description: St Joe's Freshman Taylor Funk drains open three from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Hawks' Funk sinks deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Hawks' Taylor Funk goes down the lane and slams down the hammer.
videos.headline: Funk throws it down

videos.description: Wildcats' Mikal Bridges sinks a 3-pointer from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Villanova's Bridges knocks down a triple

videos.description: Villanova's Jalen Brunson shows off his handles and finds Omari Spellman in the corner who sinks a three.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Brunson shows off handles

videos.description: Wildcats' hits three 3-pointers, part of a 14-2 run in the second half.
videos.headline: Villanova opens second half with run

videos.description: Villanova's Mikal Bridges receives the lob from Donte DiVincenzo and throws it down for the hammer.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Bridges hammers home alley-oop

videos.description: The Wildcats set a new school-record 19 3-pointers in the 94-53 victory over Saint Joseph's.
videos.headline: Villanova sets school record for made 3s in a game
